<p>A <b>general utility van</b> (<b>GUV</b>) is a type of rail vehicle buil=
t by <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_Rail" title=3D"Britis=
h Rail">British Rail</a> primarily for transporting mail and parcels. They =
were used by both <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rail_Express_Sys=
tems" title=3D"Rail Express Systems">Rail Express Systems</a> and <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Railtrack" title=3D"Railtrack">Railtrack<=
/a>. <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colas_Rail" title=3D"Colas Ra=
il">Colas Rail</a> and some <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Train_=
operating_company" title=3D"Train operating company">train operating compan=
ies</a> still use them.
</p>
